comments: Very good class, professor Sprang pushes you to be creative and wants you to do very well. He gives great feedback on projects all you have to do is ask.

He is an amazing photography instructor! I\'ve taken two classes with him so far, and wish I could take more. He pushes you to do better work, and offers advice on how to improve your skills. He is an effective communicator and explains things crystal clear. I improve by leaps and bounds in his class, and highly recommend him to others as well.

So far so good, It is more involved than what I thought a photography class would be. He seems very fair, and this is a class I look forward to. It is a break from lectures, and a chance for me to be creative.
he gives you breaks and doesnt exspect everything to be perfect and hes easy to get along with
